reviews.name: Insten 6' Gold Plated High-Speed HDMI Cable with Ethernet
reviews.reviewText: Please don't fall for the hype about "better" digital cables. A digital signal only requires a clear path in order to transfer the information from your blu-ray player to your TV. There's absolutely no reason to spend your money on some "Monstrously" overpriced cable. All you need is a cable that meets the latest requirements of the HDMI association. Save yourself some cash and buy a new blu-ray disc instead of wasting your money on voodoo technology claims.
reviews.title: Save Your Money!!!
